{"iti80:0.1":"Itivuttaka 80 ","iti80:0.2":"Tikanipata ","iti80:0.3":"Catutthavagga ","iti80:0.4":"Vitakkasutta ","iti80:1.1":"Vuttanhetam bhagavata vuttamarahatati me sutam: ","iti80:2.1":"“Tayome, bhikkhave, akusalavitakka. ","iti80:2.2":"Katame tayo? ","iti80:2.3":"Anavannattipatisamyutto vitakko, labhasakkarasilokapatisamyutto vitakko, paranuddayatapatisamyutto vitakko. ","iti80:2.4":"Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo akusalavitakka”ti. ","iti80:2.5":"Etamattham bhagava avoca. ","iti80:2.6":"Tatthetam iti vuccati: ","iti80:3.1":"“Anavannattisamyutto, ","iti80:3.2":"labhasakkaragaravo; ","iti80:3.3":"Sahanandi amaccehi, ","iti80:3.4":"ara samyojanakkhaya. ","iti80:4.1":"Yo ca puttapasum hitva, ","iti80:4.2":"Vivahe samharani ca; ","iti80:4.3":"Bhabbo so tadiso bhikkhu, ","iti80:4.4":"Phutthum sambodhimuttaman”ti. ","iti80:5.1":"Ayampi attho vutto bhagavata, iti me sutanti. ","iti80:5.2":"Pathamam. "}